title: Bach, JS and Sons - Concertos and Duets - Hogwood, Rousset
description:
The Bach Family: Keyboard Duets.

Keyboard duets by the Bach family (JS, WF, CPE, JC) performed on harpsichords, clavichords, and square pianos by Christopher Hogwood and Christophe Rousset. Be aware: the clavichord is a very quiet instrument; the middle section of this disc is meant to sound that soft. These brilliant recordings were released by L'Oiseau-Lyre in 1996.

Please enjoy.
